These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop
2 different games are played: go, poker
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony
City: boston, miami
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, siglo
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
3. the person playing poker is not the person traveling to boston##6
4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
5. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
6. the siglo-smoker is not the person who growsrose##6
7. the fan of d&b is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday      | february   | march      |
| Music-Genre          | hip-hop | d&b   |
| Game         | poker    | go |
| Pet           | guinea-pig     | pony    |
| City   | miami    | boston       |
| Cigar   | montecristo    | siglo        |
| Flower     | rose     | sunflower        |

